OL,3,CThe 5k run in its second year helping
OL,4,Cthose who've lost
OL,6,FBrandon's Dad, Nick Sutton said, "Some
OL,7,Fgood needed to come from obviously
OL,8,Ftragic circumstances" and that the run
OL,9,Fwas a testament to who Brandon was.
OL,11,FThe teenager was in his second year on
OL,12,Fthe Burton Albion Football and
OL,13,FEducation Course and money raised from
OL,14,Fthese runs will allow Burton Albion
OL,15,FCommunity Trust to develop a Young
OL,16,FPersons Bereavement help point.
