OL,3,CThe 5k run in its second year helping
OL,4,Cthose who've lost
OL,6,FAs well as that there are Brandon
OL,7,FBoxes available. Each contains items
OL,8,Fto help deal with loss and these have
OL,9,Fbeen handed to schools and those who
OL,10,Fare grieving.
OL,12,FContaining things like a blanket, a
OL,13,Fteddy and a grief journal to write
OL,14,Fthoughts about feelings, they've made
OL,15,Fa real difference. One boy, Kenzie,
OL,16,Ftold ITV News Central that it had
OL,17,Fgiven him a distraction from the
OL,18,Fthought of losing someone.
