OL,3,CThe 5k run in its second year helping
OL,4,Cthose who've lost
OL,6,FThe family are also working with St.
OL,7,FGiles Hospice, with Family Support
OL,8,FPractitioner Ali Callear saying that
OL,9,Fthe boxes help children and young
OL,10,Fpeople talk about a difficult and
OL,11,Femotional topic, whilst also offering
OL,12,Fcomfort to those going through a
OL,13,Fdifficult time.
OL,15,FTens of people turned out in the heat
OL,16,Fto either run or walk the distance
OL,17,Fwith plenty of smiles and red faces at
OL,18,Fthe end. Some of those running and
OL,19,Ftaking part in the now annual event
OL,20,Fhave been inspired to continue running
OL,21,Ffor charity.
